    .row
      .column
        .card
          a.textj(href='/')
            p.textj COMMON ADMISSION TEST
      .column
        .card
          a.textj(href='/')
            p.textj UNION PUBLIC SERVICE COMMISSION
      .column
        .card
          a.textj(href='/')
            p.textj GRADUATE APTITUDES TEST IN ENGINEERING
  section
    div(style='margin-top: 70px; text-align: center; color: white')
      p(style='font-size: 30px') POPULAR COURSES
    .pop
      .pop1
        p(style='font-size: 30px') Engineering
        ul(style='margin-top: 25px; font-size: 25px')
          li
            p Two Year Integrated Classroom Course for
            p Class XI to XII, JEE (Main &amp; Advanced)
          li(style='margin-top: 9px')
            p One Year Integrated Classroom Course for
            p Class XII, JEE (Main &amp; Advanced)
      .pop1
        p(style='font-size: 30px') Medical
        ul(style='margin-top: 25px; font-size: 25px')
          li
            p Two Year Integrated Classroom Course for
            p Class XI to XII, NEET
          li(style='margin-top: 9px')
            p One Year Integrated Classroom Course for
            p Class XII, NEET
      .pop2
        p(style='font-size: 30px') CAT
        ul(style='margin-top: 25px; font-size: 25px')
          li
            p Long-term CAT course of duration 12-15 months
          li(style='margin-top: 9px')
            p CAT Crash courses of duration 2-3 months
      .pop2
        p(style='font-size: 30px') FOUNDATION COURSES
        ul(style='margin-top: 25px; font-size: 25px')
          li
            p One-Year Integrated Classroom Course for
            p Olympiads and Class IX
          li(style='margin-top: 9px')
            p One-Year Integrated Classroom Course for
            p Olympiads, NTSE &amp; Class X
  section
    div(style='margin-top: 70px; text-align: center; color: white')
      p(style='font-size: 30px')
        | What makes Foundation us the smartest choice?
    .advant
      div(style='margin-top: 60px; text-align: center; color: white')
        p(style='margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 24px')
          | ABOUT FOUNDATION COURSES
      marquee.marq(behavior='alternative' scrollamount='2' onmouseover='this.stop();' onmouseout='this.start();' width='65%' direction='up' height='300px')
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 1. Building a Strong Academic Foundation: Foundation courses provide
          | students with a solid grounding in essential subjects
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 2. Bridging Knowledge Gaps: Foundation courses are especially
          | helpful for students who come from different educational
          | backgrounds.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 3. Exploring Interests and Aptitudes: Foundation courses often cover
          | a broad range of subjects, allowing students to explore different
          | fields
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 4. Increased Confidence and Motivation: Foundation courses give
          | students a sense of accomplishment and confidence as they acquire
          | new knowledge and skills
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 5. Higher Success Rates: Institutes that implement foundation
          | courses often observe higher success rates among students
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 6. Developing Critical Thinking and Problem-Solving Skills:
          | Foundation courses emphasize critical thinking, analytical
          | reasoning, and problem-solving skills.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 7. Enhancing Communication and Language Skills: Many foundation
          | courses focus on improving students&apos; communication and language
          | skills
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 8. Smooth Transition to Higher Education: Foundation courses provide
          | a smoother transition from secondary education to higher education.
    .advant
      div(style='\
      margin-top: 60px;\
      text-align: center;\
      color: white;\
      ')
        p(style='margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 24px') OUR FORTE
      marquee.marq(behavior='alternative' scrollamount='2' onmouseover='this.stop();' onmouseout='this.start();' width='65%' direction='up' height='300px')
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 1. Expert Guidance and Teaching: We have experienced faculty members
          | who specialize in entrance exam preparation.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 2. Comprehensive Study Materials: We provide students with
          | well-researched and comprehensive study materials that cover the
          | entire syllabus of the entrance exams.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 3. Mock Tests and Practice Sessions: We conduct regular mock tests
          | and practice sessions to familiarize students with the exam pattern,
          | time management techniques, and the types of questions they can
          | expect.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 4. Doubt Clearing Sessions: We offer doubt clearing sessions where
          | students can seek clarification on difficult concepts or questions.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 5. Performance Analysis and Feedback: We provide students with
          | feedback and performance analysis based on their mock tests and
          | practice sessions.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 6. Time Management and Exam Strategy: We emphasize the importance of
          | effective time management and exam strategy.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 7. Access to Additional Resources: We may provide students with
          | access to additional resources such as online study portals,
          | libraries, and digital learning platforms.
        p(style='font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 25px')
          | 8. Past Year Question Papers and Analysis: We provide students with
          | past year question papers of the entrance exams.
